## Layouts

Always use one of these â€” never inject `<head>` or JSON-LD manually:

- **`PageLayout.astro`**: Use for all content pages. Props: `title`, `description`, `locale`, `schema`, `breadcrumbs`, `heroTitle`, `heroSubtitle`.
- **`BaseLayout.astro`**: Lower-level wrapper (head + header + footer). `PageLayout` uses this internally.

## Adding Content

- **New location**: Append to `src/data/locations.ts` â€” 900 programmatic pages auto-generate.
- **New service**: Create `src/content/services/{slug}.json`, add import + array entry in `src/data/services.ts`.

## Build Obfuscation

Production build renames `--tw-*` â†’ `--c-*`, Tailwind layer names â†’ generic names, `/_astro/` â†’ `/static/`. HTML comments are stripped. No source maps. Do not reference internal Tailwind vars.

